The paper deals with training stochastic neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on using pre-trained parameters of deterministic deep neural networks, which is a common technique in machine learning and neural networks research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, and cs.SY.
